sect2.para:
--sysconfdir=&gnome-etc-dir;: This switch puts
    configuration files in &gnome-etc-dir;
    instead of $GNOME_PREFIX/etc.

seglistitem.seg:
&gnome-etc-dir;/gconf/gconf.xml.defaults/{,desktop/}{,schemas/}apps/{too many to list}
        and the following subdirectories of $GNOME_PREFIX/:
        include/gnome-window-settings-2.0,
        lib/{lib, nautilus, window-manager-settings},
        share/{{,gnome/help/,omf}control-center-2.0,
        gnome/{cursor-fonts,vfolders}}
